Class YADAQueryResult

  • java.lang.Object

    • Field Detail

      • qname

        private String qname
        The query name of the query from which this result is generated and to which this result is attached.

      • results

        private List<Object> results
        The list of query results, in raw form, i.e. ResultSet, String

      • convertedResults

        private List<Object> convertedResults
        The list of converted query results. These objects are to be returned to the requestor.

      • convertedHeader

        private List<String> convertedHeader
        The converted (mapped) header, i.e., list of column names. This list is the same for the entire result. These objects are to be returned to the requestor.
        Since:
        6.1.0

      • countResults

        private List<Object> countResults
        The list of results of count queries. These results typically end up as values corresponding to total keys in RESULTSET objects inside YADA json.

      • parameters

        private List<YADAParam> parameters
        The list of configuration parameters

      • totalResultCount

        private int totalResultCount
        The number of rows processed across all iterations of the YADAQuery

      • globalHarmonyMap

        private org.json.JSONObject globalHarmonyMap
        The container of field names to support merged result sets
        Since:
        6.1.0
